package practiseproblem;
import java.util.*;
public class HCF {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		// TODO Auto-generated method stub
		Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
		long X=sc.nextLong();
		long Y=sc.nextLong();
		X=(X>0)?X:-X;
		Y=(Y>0)?Y:-Y;
		while(X!=Y){
			if(X>Y) {
				X=X-Y;
				System.out.println("#"+X);
			}
			else {
				Y=Y-X;
				System.out.println("*"+Y);
			}
		}
		System.out.println(X);
		sc.close();

	}

}
